{
  "title": "Gentle Earthy Malaysian Beef Kidney Curry",
  "description": "A comforting and earthy Malaysian curry featuring beef kidney in a rich and creamy sauce, perfect for a sick day, and made without nuts for a nut-free friendly option, with a hint of sweetness from palm sugar candy.",
  "cuisine": "Malaysian",
